{"tid":1610770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 回 ］冇gear唔好上前線","createTime":"2019-10-01T20:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T20:18:58.000Z","uid":235446,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"643e089fada69245e7fea0c93624e5eab76c598b","tid":1610770,"uid":235446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:03:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我係其中一個叫冇裝既唔好上前線既人。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知你地點諗，我心目中對前線既定義係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">子彈横飛</span></span></strong>，得個3M基本眼罩既你其實都要自求多福，我試過幾次俾狗𣈴頭射，好彩有時有傘有時有偱頂住。而且，有好大機會一日之後就要換罐。所以如果冇gear上前真係唔建議⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n612我未有gear，硬食TG既我係口水鼻涕眼淚一齊岀，失曬方向，身邊仲有人頭暈腳軟甚至哮喘發作。<br />\n<br />\n 試諗下，如果現家你地咁，冇gear，我地點救，我希望FA係可以救中彈既手足，929個日子再次彈橫飛，幾乎每半分鐘就有一個手足失去知覺咁被FA抬走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再者，前線係陣形上係有部署架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 萬一啲狗衝前，你地狀態又唔ok，咁點跑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(仲未計如果岀水炮車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">不過，我好感激你地願意踏出第一步上前，不過希望你地可以保護好自己，不受傷不被捕！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人，加油</strong></span>"},{"pid":"67ad35bdf32d8e859531618b5a3102039b539c43","tid":1610770,"uid":242726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:06:08.000Z","msg":"無gear真係唔好企咁前 頂住前面啲人向後走<br />\n<br />\n留啲距離比前面向後就跑"},{"pid":"d2a0d39a862fc917062443873f09c722d88d59a4","tid":1610770,"uid":235446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:08:13.000Z","msg":"搵唔返個原po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3209e06b9967e6a9fc278b40201ea22f92ab6c","tid":1610770,"uid":235446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:18:58.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}